{"title":"朝鲜解放战争胜利十周年颂","authors":["黄炎培"],"dates":[{"year":1963,"month":7,"day":27}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"朝鲜解放战争胜利十周年颂"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黄炎培"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（一）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鲜红的朝阳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"朗照着我国的东方。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我曾三渡扶桑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"亲见那些可爱的朝鲜青年，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在暴日压迫下，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不许升大学，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不许穿军士服装，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"并不许穿警察服装。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在我气愤填胸下，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"所有我作品，一概被禁止发行。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（二）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一九二六年杭州的春天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"北高峰下，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"初阳台畔流连。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"忽见，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二青年露宿台边。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"问何为宿此？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"答：祖国是朝鲜。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"暴日迫使逃亡，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"同行二十多青年。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"愿读中学，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我就索取名单，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"介绍每校两青年，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"学膳费都免。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不久，我也政治流亡了。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我很想念这可爱的二十多青年，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在他们祖国解放战争中作何贡献？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（三）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鲜红的朝阳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"阳光四射，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"朗照到世界的东方。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十年以前，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"英雄的朝鲜人民呀！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"难忘！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"难忘！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我和你，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是双方血和肉凝结而成的兄弟之邦。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"世界不少旧的还有新的怪现象。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"努力！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在世界反帝怒潮高度汹涌下，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在朝鲜英雄人民不断跃进下，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我敢断言："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不久的将来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"阳光遍照着统一全疆。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"1963．7．26．"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":3,"page_end":3}